{"type":"message","id":"212332f6","parentId":"753ce4e9","timestamp":"2026-03-21T11:19:10.171Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The authentication is working. Let me provide a summary of what was accomplished.","thinkingSignature":"13964034eb0a5d93e5d04fce68cc855b91a904b50eb8b38767dbb35ec7d8d316"},{"type":"text","text":"## 任务完成汇报\n\n### 问题诊断\n本地 Docker TradingAgents API (localhost:8000) 的认证问题已解决。\n\n**原因分析:**\n- 数据库中的 token 格式不正确或未被正确使用\n- 原有 token (`sk-minimax-local-test`) 不符合 API 要求的 `ta-sk-` 前缀格式\n- API 需要通过邮箱验证码流程获取 JWT 访问令牌，或创建持久化的 API token\n\n### 解决方案\n通过以下步骤解决了认证问题:\n\n1. **邮箱验证流程**: 使用有效邮箱格式（如 `admin@local.com`）调用 `/v1/auth/request-code` 获取验证码\n2. **验证获取 JWT**: 用验证码调用 `/v1/auth/verify-code` 获取 JWT access_token\n3. **创建持久 Token**: 用 JWT 调用 `POST /v1/tokens` 创建符合 `ta-sk-` 格式的持久化 API token\n\n### 当前配置\n- **API URL**: `http://localhost:8000`\n- **API Token**: `ta-sk-tTFWTVGM7TVX-3VOjgDiGw6MexVvra-24RM9yTh5PDjET8QkL7-tscRXbnmi-ptalIw7zSblFoJPffn2oWbaLA`\n\n### 验证结果\n- `/v1/analyze` 端点返回 200，任务提交成功 ✅\n- 数据接口（如 `/v1/market/hot-stocks`）正常工作 ✅\n\n配置已保存至 `TRADINGAGENTS_CONFIG.md`。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":44729,"output":339,"cacheRead":32187,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":77255,"cost":{"input":0.013418699999999999,"output":0.00040679999999999997,"cacheRead":0.0009656099999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.01479111}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774091942275}}
